                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Key Learnings</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-category text-info mb-1">Authentication & Authorization</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Integrated ASP.NET Core Identity for user authentication and role
                                management</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Implemented invitation-based registration</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Role-based access control for teachers, students, and administrators
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Features include login, logout, invitation link regeneration, and
                                password change</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="card-category text-info mb-1">Database</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Used Entity Framework Core to work with relational data models,
                                including many-to-many relationships</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Managed schema changes through EF Core data migrations</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Implemented data searching, filtering, and pagination</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="card-category text-info mb-1">Full Stack Development</h3>
