                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Applied Bootstrap and a template for UI styling</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p class="card-text">Added JavaScript for interactive and dynamic front-end behavior</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

